high_descs: Walk two steps forward, turn left for one step, turn right for one step, turn left and walk to the bathtub and stop.
Pick up the purple fabric closest to the pink soap, in the bathtub.
Turn right and for two steps and turn right for one step and raise the fabric up.
Put the fabric on top of the toilet tank, above the flushing handle.
Turn right for three steps, turn right and go over to the bathtub.
Take out the purple fabric from the bathtub.
Turn right and walk four steps, turn right for one step and hold the fabric up.
Put the fabric on top of the toilet tank to the right of the first fabric but position the fabric so it is standing on its end.
anns.task_desc: Put two pieces of purple fabric on top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn left, walk straight to the tub
Pick up the purple cloth in the tub
Turn right, turn right, walk straight to the toilet.
Put the purple cloth on top of the toilet
Turn right, turn right, walk straight to the tub.
Pick up the purple cloth in the tub
Turn right, turn right, walk straight to the toilet.
Put the purple cloth on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Put two purple cloths on top of the toilet

high_descs: move left to the tub
pick up a cloth from the tub
turn around and head to the toilet
place the cloth on the toilet

pick up a cloth on the tub
